quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,"Alif, Lam, Mim. (These are the names of three letters from the Arabic alphabet, probably indicating that this inimitable Revelation, the Qur'an, is made of this Arabic alphabet. Only Allah Knows their meaning here)"
  2,2,"That is the Book, there is no suspicion about it, a guidance to the pious"
  2,3,"Who believe in the Unseen, and keep up the prayer, and expend of what We have provided them"
  2,4,"And who believe in what has been sent down to you, and what has been sent down (even) before you, and they constantly have certitude in the Hereafter"
  2,5,"Those are upon guidance from their, and those are they who are the prosperers"
  2,6,"Surely, the ones who have disbelieved, it is equal to them whether you have warned them or have not warned them, they do not believe"
  2,7,Allah has set a seal on their hearts and on their hearing; and on their be-holdings (i.e. eyesights) is an envelopment. And for them is a tremendous torment